reviewText: One of my favorite movies!! Delivery was so fast I was ecstatic! Thank you!

Recommended it was funny, romantic, and understandable.
I saw it like 3 times. The storyline is fresh and realistic. Indian actors are also sexy, ad its funny when they mix the language.
I wish I could get more of my friends to give this movie a try. Easily the best Bollywood movie I have ever seen.
